title: Shiraz Shish Kabob
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small, family-run restaurant with around 20 tables for seating. Menu includes a vegetarian section with around 16 or so entrees, clearly coded green for easy reference. Includes dishes like veggie shish-kabob, falafel, dolma, khoreshteh, abgoosht, aush, sabzis, baba gannouj, hummus, tabour, and others. Note that naan is made with yogurt.
